data.description: Welcome to an inviting 4-bed, 2.5-bath residence displaying a generously sized front and a welcoming front porch. Discover a spacious living area & family room with high ceilings, abundant natural light, and durable tile flooring. The gourmet kitchen boasts granite counters, recessed and pendant lighting, paneled cabinets, mosaic tile backsplash, sleek stainless steel appliances, and an island with a breakfast bar. Lay down and relax in the main bedroom, a serene retreat offering vaulted ceilings, a private bath, and a walk-in closet. Unwind in the expansive backyard, displaying a covered patio for alfresco dining and tons of space to let your imagination run wild in creating your dream oasis. See it now!
